{"tid":1567263,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂]今次運動的關鍵是西方領袖願意大聲疾呼：我是香港人！","createTime":"2019-09-14T04:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:11:21.000Z","uid":300697,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"10d40f2e23ff3d0bdcf0081aeaaebe018540473f","tid":1567263,"uid":300697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:01:37.000Z","msg":"1961年，柏林圍牆興建使被共產東德包圍的西柏林完全成為孤島。<br />\n<br />\n1963 年，美國總統 J F Kenny 在西柏林演說，表明追求民主自由的人都是柏林人。<br />\n<br />\n因此，出現了著名的德語語句：Ich bin ein Berliner.<br />\n意思是我是柏林人。如果本地民意和國際輿論都能夠做得好，令香港人打造成為廿一世紀爭取自由民主的前線，使西方能與香港人坐上抵禦中國黨國體制的船上，是長遠能夠抗爭成功的必要關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家能夠一齊振臂高呼：<br />\nI am a HongKonger! / Ich bin ein HongKonger!<br />\n如果使用英語，國際上會比較普遍，<br />\n但如果使用德語，就會引起部份經歷過冷戰的人的共鳴。請大家好好思考一下。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2Ha9GJwlus8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2Ha9GJwlus8&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZy%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=b16129e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2Ha9GJwlus8</a>"},{"pid":"7cbf07d3a3250614f1686e2491c6e2869a287251","tid":1567263,"uid":200870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce88dfe1500d1816bc7ac751bf3806430dfba8ee","tid":1567263,"uid":200870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58c84eeb6234e7acc4325e7f2e964f4ad7e75b2","tid":1567263,"uid":200870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.g